snippet.title: UNDERSWAP Reckoning - UNDEREVENT Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
* The point of no return.

This was apart of UNDEREVENT 2024, go watch it!: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ho5jkOfUFtY

Follow our Gamejolt to get nicely updated: 
https://gamejolt.com/games/The-reckoning/879778

Being in UNDEREVENT was an awesome experience and we are honored to be able to collaborate with so much talent within the Undertale community.

NOTE: Elements in this trailer are currently outdated and will changed in the final game.

 Credits:
DUSTTRUST - Dillywolf
UNDERTALE - Toby Fox

Inspirations - Omori, Bani-chan

Trailer/Editing - Epickthan
End glitch effect and refinements - Dingyspy
Music/SFX - TheRedCrystal

#undertale #undertaleau #sans
